
Use finit state mechanism to bring menu structure
<state>



	<poweron>
	    |
	    | [default]
	    v
Vin	<disp Vin txt>		--[after a second]--> 	<display Vin Voltage value>
	    |
	    | [set-key]
	    v
Vout	<disp Vout txt>		--[after a second]--> 	<display Vout Voltage value>
	    |							|
	    | [set-key]						
	    v
Iout	<disp Iout txt>		--[after a second]--> 	<display Iout current value>
	    |
	    |
	    v
	  [vin]
